fields.description: The ID of request for delta loading. Once it is set, only data with requestId larger than the value of this property will be retrieved. The default value is 0. Type: integer (or Expression with resultType integer ).
fields.name: BaseRequestId

fields.description: Whether to exclude the records of the last request. The default value is true. Type: boolean (or Expression with resultType boolean).
fields.name: ExcludeLastRequest

fields.description: The name of the Open Hub Destination with destination type as Database Table. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: OpenHubDestinationName
